These scripts were run on a SLURM cluster. 

submit_DOS.sh (submit_spectral.sh) creates a job using the slurm_DOS.sh (slurm_spectral.sh) script.
That uses Julia to run the run_DOS.jl (run_spectral.jl) for AC.

Conductivity AC just uses the run_curr.jl script to run ana_cont. 
ana_cont is a python package, but it can be run in Julia using the PyCall package.